  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective randomized open-label pilot study to compare mycophenolate mofetil in
      combination with corticosteroid treatment and tacrolimus in combination with corticosteroid
      treatment in membranous lupus nephritis. The change in urine protein excretion will be the
      primary outcome studied. The study duration will be 24 months for each patient.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
